                            <comment id="12668776" author="fmeschbe" created="Fri, 30 Jan 2009 08:14:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Proposed patch: The state variable is not final again and set to the actual state after calling the init() method.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12669106" author="rickhall" created="Sat, 31 Jan 2009 00:59:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I committed a variant of your patch. There was no need to play around with getting the value since we were holding the lock the entire time, so I just changed the patch to just use method calls. I think this was just a refactoring omission.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
